{
  "verses": [
    {
      "verse_num": "1",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I love Yahweh, because he listens to my voice, and my cries for mercy."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "2",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Because he has turned his ear to me, therefore I will call on him as long as I live."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "3",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "The cords of death surrounded me, the pains of Sheol got a hold of me."
        },
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I found trouble and sorrow."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "4",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Then I called on Yahweh’s name:\n"
        },
        {
          "type": "prayer",
          "text": "Yahweh, I beg you, deliver my soul.",
          "speaker": "Unknown"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "5",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Yahweh is gracious and righteous. Yes, our God is merciful."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "6",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Yahweh preserves the simple. I was brought low, and he saved me."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "7",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Return to your rest, my soul, for Yahweh has dealt bountifully with you."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "8",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "For you have delivered my soul from death, my eyes from tears,"
        },
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "and my feet from falling."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "9",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I will walk before Yahweh in the land of the living."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "10",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I believed, therefore I said,"
        },
        {
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "I was greatly afflicted.",
          "speaker": "Unknown"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "11",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I said in my haste,\n"
        },
        {
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "All people are liars.",
          "speaker": "Unknown"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "12",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "What will I give to Yahweh for all his benefits toward me?"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "13",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I will take the cup of salvation, and call on Yahweh’s name."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "14",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I will pay my vows to Yahweh, yes, in the presence of all his people."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "15",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Precious in Yahweh’s sight is the death of his saints."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "16",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Yahweh, truly I am your servant. I am your servant, the son of your servant girl.\nYou have freed me from my chains."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "17",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I will offer to you the sacrifice of thanksgiving, and will call on Yahweh’s name."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "18",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I will pay my vows to Yahweh, yes, in the presence of all his people,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "19",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "in the courts of Yahweh’s house, in the middle of you, Jerusalem. Praise Yah!"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    }
  ]
}